## 3. MCP Ecosystem Adoption

### AI Models and Frameworks

- **Anthropic (Claude)** â€“ Full support for MCP in desktop version.
- **OpenAI** â€“ Agent SDK and API support.
- **Baidu Maps** â€“ Geolocation via MCP.
- **Blender MCP** â€“ Natural language-based 3D model generation.

### Developer Tools

- **Replit** â€“ MCP tools in coding environments.
- **Microsoft Copilot Studio** â€“ Integrated MCP-based tools.
- **Sourcegraph Cody** â€“ MCP via OpenCTX.
- **Codeium** â€“ MCP-enabled cross-system coding tasks.
- **Cursor** â€“ Composer integration for MCP-based execution.
- **Cline** â€“ VS Code agent with MCP support.

### IDEs / Editors

- **Zed, JetBrains, Theia, Emacs, OpenSumi, Windsurf Editor** â€“ Support for MCP-enabled commands and tools.

### Cloud & Platforms

- **Cloudflare** â€“ Remote MCP hosting and OAuth integration.
- **Block (Square)** â€“ Enhances financial data processing.
- **Stripe** â€“ MCP-based API exposure for payment systems.

### Web Automation and Data

